headline: Trump Calls for Release of ‘Pertinent’ Epstein Grand Jury Material Following WSJ Article
summary: The president threatened to sue the newspaper and News Corp for publishing an article about a letter bearing his name that was included in a 2003 birthday album for Jeffrey Epstein.

headline: Trump Seeks Release of Grand Jury Documents in Epstein Case
summary: (Bloomberg) -- US President Donald Trump authorized the Justice Department to seek the release of grand jury testimony from the prosecution of Jeffrey Epstein, bowing to mounting pressure from his supporters for more transparency about the late, disgraced financier.
